text: Chang Taekwon -Do are really friendly and welcoming and have a really engaging and fun way of not only teaching Tae Kwon Do but teaching about the body, health and wellbeing and how to deal with bullying. I would recommend Chang Blackbelt Academy to anyone that is looking to get not only their kids into martial arts but themselves as well.
Great coach with passionate to teach, responsibility to lead our kids are excellent. Great knowledge and experience in martial art which benefit our kids for their development.
Not only Coach Nelson teach the kids on taekwondo skills for the grading, but also share the correct ways of self-defense and to guide trainees from misusing martial arts.
